des:
Amazon Alexa voice control enables you to manage and adjust elements across your DARWIN Home Wellness Intelligence ecosystem. DARWIN is designed to enhance your health and wellbeing through elements including Circadian Lighting, Responsive Air Purification, and an Enhanced Sleep System. With the DARWIN Native skill for Amazon Alexa, you can control devices that are connected to DARWIN via Amazon Alexa, including smart lights and blackout blinds. 

This skill requires the smart home solution powered by DARWIN, including the DARWIN Hub and edge devices. You will need to log in with your DARWIN username and password, the same username and password you use for the DARWIN app.
